data.description: Very fresh and situated just right toward the top of a gently sloping 2.63 acres in the heart of Warner Springs' wine country, Sunshine Summit, Holcomb Village. Fantastic open layout, light and bright and clean! Two bedrooms and a ton of space - plenty of room to re-arrange and re-work into the layout you desire. And did you see the GARAGE!?? A luxury in these parts, you already have a fab two car garage PLUS room for another workshop, barn, additional dwelling unit/s ... Warner Springs enjoys a spectacular four seasons, never too extreme, mellow breezes, surprising micro-climates, and no matter where it is in the world your life makes you venture to and from for work and so on, the hardest part of the commute in any direction is leaving home. This elevation provides a Mediterranean vibe, as evidenced by the nearby lavender farms, olive orchards, and the North Mountain Wine Trail. Many locals thrive through their work in agritourism, hosting via glamping or vacation rentals, cottage industry, or telecommuting/working from home.
